      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not even about \"help\" anymore. helping a shell doesn't make sense. the person who had the capacity to move forward, the one who cared about the future... they're just gone. it's like watching a ghost inhabit a person. how am i supposed to \"reach out\" when there's no one left inside to actually do the reaching? it just feels like a waste of time to keep pretending.",
