      "content": "but that's the thing... it's not a fight. it's more like a funeral. the version of me that mattered is already deceased. everything else is just... leftover noise. it feels so wrong to just keep dragging this empty weight around when the actual person is already gone. wouldn't it be more honest to just let the physical part catch up to the truth?",
